{"tid":1080864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拍AV遭尪抓包慘離婚 「最強人妻」籌百萬拍全裸寫真告別宅粉","createTime":"2019-03-28T01:42:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T02:18:53.000Z","uid":32511,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"77217e56b0fa0cd27a4682c9c6692e49da1f270f","tid":1080864,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T01:42:16.000Z","msg":"39歲日本AV女優佐佐木明希，有「最強人妻」封號，去年宣布將於2019年4月引退，並在網上揪影迷集資，拍攝最後的全裸寫真。<br />\n<br />\n佐佐木明希與老公育有2個孩子，2015年瞞家人進暗黑圈拍片，去年拍片被發現，離婚後，她一肩扛起扶養小孩責任，12月在部落格透露，AV生涯僅到2019年4月，坦言引退想法早在1年前前就有，同時也感謝粉絲這些年來的支持。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hqO61W1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhqO61W1.jpg&h=d715bf42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佐佐木明希向粉絲集資拍告別AV的全裸寫真。（翻攝自網路）<br />\n<br />\n佐佐木明希宣布引退後，立即在網路上揪集資，預告將拍攝最後的全裸寫真，活動共426位粉絲參與，籌得763萬日圓（約台幣214萬），超過原先所預期的250萬日圓（約台幣70萬），該引退作會以新作加精選形式販售，封面打著「我會做回一個普通的主婦」宣傳標語，吸引粉絲搶購。"},{"pid":"fca7b08f43874a479c6b704cd3777e260da990b0","tid":1080864,"uid":172464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T01:48:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab2b45c5dbe0db10cf92cc998eaf26f42c72bcab","tid":1080864,"uid":53687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T01:50:24.000Z","msg":"佢身邊啲人唔睇av咩？呢啲嘢點瞞？<br />\n我就真係唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c890fc90e5049f01a13cee4dadd7f6101efeae","tid":1080864,"uid":67346,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T01:54:26.000Z","msg":"個尪字係咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a69f0058de84879184d2947b23b690883de36c8b","tid":1080864,"uid":63909,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T01:54:46.000Z","msg":"佐佐木明希堅正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"h